Text: 'Tis truly great - I'm glad Sandy continued on her own after Fotheringay had their short run. Could you re-seed for a few days, though - so the 4 of us halted at 99.7% could get the last 2 missing pieces? Much obliged, Alltattooed!

Great album, needs reseeding as only have 99.7%, which is a shame.
floppyowl
